When working with a virtual machine on a hypervisor that handles I/O scheduling, whichscheduling mechanism is suggested for virtual machines?
A)  cfq
B)  noop
C)  timed
D)  vm- opt
B
B. The noop scheduling algorithm is recommended for virtual machines on a hypervisorhost that performs the I/O scheduling. Of the other options shown, cfq is the defaultscheduling algorithm. The other two options are not valid.
